\c 11
\s Hushe hwakanaka hwaMesiasi
\p
\v 1 Zvino pahunde yaJese pachabuda bukira, davi, rinobuda pamidzi yake, richabereka zvibereko.
\v 2 Mweya waJehovha uchagara pamusoro pake, mweya wenjere nowokungwara, mweya wamano nesimba, mweya wokuziva nokutya Jehovha.
\p
\v 3 Mufaro wake uchava pakutya Jehovha; haangatongi nokungoona nameso bedzi, kana kupa mhosva nokungonzwa nenzeve dzake bedzi;
\v 4 asi achatongera varombo nokururama, achatambira vanyoro venyika mhaka dzavo zvakarurama; acharova nyika neshamhu yomuromo wake, achavauraya vakaipa nomweya wemiromo yake.
\v 5 Kururama richava bhanhire rechiuno chake, kutendeka richava bhanhire rezvidza zvake.
\v 6 Bere richagara negwayana, ingwe ichavata pasi nembudzana, nemhuru nomwana weshumba nechipfuwo chakakora pamwechete; uye mwana muduku achadzitungamirira.
\v 7 Mhou nebere zvichafura; vana vadzo vachavata pamwechete; shumba ichadya uswa senzombe.
\p
\v 8 Mwana anomwa, achatamba pamwena wenyoka, uye mwana akarumurwa achapinza ruoko rwake mubako remvumbi.
\p
\v 9 Hazvingakuvadzi kana kuparadza pagomo rangu rose dzvene, nokuti nyika yose ichazara nokuziva Jehovha, sezvinofukidza mvura pasi pegungwa.
\p
\v 10 Nezuva iro mudzi waJese, iwo umirepo somureza wavanhu, uchatsvakwa namarudzi avanhu; nzvimbo yake yokuzorora ichava nembiri.
\p
\v 11 Zvino nezuva iro Ishe achatambanudzazve ruoko rwake kechipiri kuti adzikinure vakasara vavanhu vake, ivo vanenge vasara, vari paAsiria,
\p nePatirosi, neKushi, neErami, neShinari, neHamati, nokuzvitsuwa zvegungwa.
\v 12 Achasimudzira marudzi mureza, nokuunganidza vadzingwa vaIsiraeri, no
\p kuunenid
\v 74 )%Judtta vakaparadzirwa
\s kumativi mana enyika.
\p
\v 13 Ipapo godo ravaEfuremu richapera, navanomanikidza vaJudha vachaparadzwa; vaEfuremu havangagodori vaJudha, navaJudha havangamanikidzi vaEfuremu.
\v 14 Asi vachabhururukira pamusoro pamafudzi avaFirisitia kumavirazuva, vachapambara pamwechete vana vamabvazuva; vachatambanudzira maoko avo kuvaEdhomu navaMoabhi, navana vaAmoni vachavateerera.
\v 15 Jehovha achaparadza chose muromo wegungwa reIjipiti, achasimudzira ruoko rwake pamusoro poRwizi nemhepo yake inopisa, ndokururova ruite hova nomwe, ayambuse vanhu vakafuka shangu.
\v 16 Vanhu vake vakasara, vakasara Asiria, vachava nenzira huru; sezvazvakaitirwa Isiraeri nezuva ravakabuda munyika yeIj ipiti.
